# Web client (`apps/web`)

## State

- `state/gameStore.ts` — calls `@all-according-to-plan/game-engine`, stores `GameState`
- `state/motionStore.ts` — visual cues only (`play`, `draw`, `pendingPlayExit`, archive flash)
- `state/roundSnapshot.ts` — cycle revert
- Never duplicate gameplay rules in components

## Card UX

- Operational hand: `CardBar` + `HandDirectiveCard` — click card to play (no separate Play button)
- Active programs: `PlayedCards` — **assets only**
- Event history: `DirectiveArchive` in advisor panel — **events only**
- Shared layout: `components/cards/DirectiveCard.tsx`

## Motion & input

- Animations must not block play; use `pendingPlayExit` for exit animations
- Prefer transform/opacity; avoid Framer `layout` on hand strip
- Respect `useMotionPrefs()` / reduced motion

## Audio

- Singleton: `audio/AudioManager.ts`
- Unlock on first user gesture via `AudioProvider`
- See `AUDIO.md` for bed/layers

## Imports

Use `@/` alias for web-internal paths. Workspace packages for engine/shared.

## Aesthetic

Authoritarian command UI per `DESIGN.md` — not fantasy TCG, not neon arcade.
